#     snx_link_adam

#  Purpose:
#     Generate linker (ld) arguments for linking SNX library.

#  Language:
#     Bourne Shell

#  Type of Module:
#     Shell script.

#  Description:
#     This script should be invoked when linking against the SNX library.
#     Use -user when supplying all the user replaceable NCAR functions.

